1
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:05,359
Officer

2
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:06,959
It can't be Wen Jie

3
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:08,439
He has already confessed everything clearly

4
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:09,920
It was while you were away

5
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,719
that he secretly used Liang Shichu's computer

6
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,120
to access the game's backend

7
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:15,319
and planted prohibited code in the game

8
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,239
Impossible

9
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,200
The three of us are so close

10
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,439
Besides

11
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,439
Wen Jie never took classes seriously

12
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:24,079
I even wrote his coding homework for him

13
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:25,760
How could he have the skill to do that

14
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,000
According to his statement

15
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,920
he learned basic programming online by himself

16
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,480
and there were so-called experts

17
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,719
who helped him modify the exploit code

18
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,799
There must be more to this

19
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,159
He might have been forced

20
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:36,680
Where is the evidence

21
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,280
Where is the evidence of coercion

22
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,719
Startup teams falling out over profits

23
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:46,719
we've seen plenty of that

24
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:49,120
If you want to go in and ask him face-to-face

25
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,280
go fill out a form at the window on the first floor

26
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:53,519
If you want to keep arguing with me here

27
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:54,799
then please leave

28
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,159
No, wait

29
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:55,480
Hey

30
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,719
Sorry, Officer

31
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,840
Sorry to trouble you

32
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,919
Wen Jie

33
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,520
Wen Jie

34
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:14,919
Look at us

35
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,080
What exactly happened

36
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:18,639
What is going on

37
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:20,800
The three of us are brothers

38
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:21,719
Stop talking

39
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:23,960
I did it

40
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,599
I let you down

41
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,759
Please stop asking, okay

42
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:29,639
Impossible

43
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,039
You couldn't have done something like this

44
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,319
Is there something going on

45
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,159
Don't hide it

46
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:41,759
Say something

47
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,719
There's nothing else

48
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,159
That's just how it is

49
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:49,840
It was just me

50
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,719
I was jealous of your skills

51
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,159
Jealous that you can write code

52
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,319
and make games

53
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,520
And then you

54
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,199
didn't include me when starting the tech company

55
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,280
What kind of bullshit is that

56
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,599
Fan

57
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:09,719
Liang

58
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,960
Stop talking

59
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,520
Don't come back, okay

60
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,439
Wen Jie

61
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,599
Wen Jie

62
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,080
Wen Jie, remember this

63
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,159
Wen Jie, remember

64
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,199
I, Chen Fan, will always consider you my brother

65
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:29,080
There's definitely something fishy about this

66
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,120
It's definitely not simple

67
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:41,960
Mr. Liu

68
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,080
Chen Fan is now missing Luo Wenjie

69
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,319
his right-hand man

70
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:46,400
and he's dived headfirst into

71
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,360
the banned Mecha Shanghai game case

72
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,280
He's severely weakened now

73
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,599
This pledge of loyalty of mine

74
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,319
your company should be satisfied, right

75
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:57,919
Good

76
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,199
Listen, Chen

77
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,400
Luo Wenjie's fate will be yours

78
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,080
If you know what's good for you, don't try to be a hero

79
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,080
Just be a student and stay in your lane

80
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,159
This trick again

81
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,759
I know without the anonymity

82
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,079
that this was sent by Long's people

83
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,560
Wen Jie is already in this state

84
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,720
Ruochu, Liang

85
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,240
I can't let anyone else around me get hurt

86
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,920
Let's investigate Long's background first

87
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:43,920
Mr. Liu

88
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,800
Whatever you order me to do

89
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,240
I will do my best

90
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,600
It's a project linked to the company's overseas business

91
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,160
The risk is a bit high

92
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,279
but once it's done

93
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,120
you'll rise to the top

94
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,079
I remember in my previous life

95
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,079
what I fought to the death to protect

96
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:02,279
was the evidence of this Long family smuggling case

97
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,519
The Longs started by recruiting their own people

98
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,879
to expand their smuggling network

99
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,759
Manager Liu and Zhou Honghai

100
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,800
must be discussing this very case

101
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,279
But Brother Honghai...

102
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:25,279
After all, he watched me grow up.

103
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:28,560
I can't let his life be ruined just like that.

104
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,959
I need to gather evidence again.

105
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,000
And change the outcome.

106
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,279
Ruochu.

107
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:44,000
Since I know the Long Group is behind this,

108
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,279
I must take precautions.

109
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:48,319
And protect my Ruochu.

110
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,160
Ruochu.

111
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,759
The law firm where Ruochu interns is surrounded by shops.

112
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,199
That makes things easier.

113
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,279
Hey, Xiao Pang.

114
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,639
We're not buying houses today.

115
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,920
I want you to help me buy a few shops.

116
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,439
Oh, right.

117
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,800
Buy some cameras for me too.

118
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,600
Install them at the entrances of the street-side shops.

119
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:19,639
The more hidden, the better.

120
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,879
Thanks for your trouble.

121
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,199
Hey, Ruochu.

122
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,519
Are you packed?

123
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,879
Alright, I'm coming to the dorm to pick you up right now.

124
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,399
Come, come on in.

125
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:34,879
Okay.

126
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,519
You rest first, I'll go tidy up.

127
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,319
Okay.

128
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,439
Let me, let me, let me.

129
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,720
Go and rest.

130
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,199
Well, I can't just do nothing.

131
00:06:58,519 --> 00:07:00,279
You cleaned the apartment,

132
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:01,800
You installed surveillance,

133
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,480
And just changed the lock.

134
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,480
Right?

135
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,240
Speaking of the surveillance,

136
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:06,720
Let me show you.

137
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:07,439
What?

138
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,319
You'll see.

139
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,120
Come here.

140
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,519
What is it?

141
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,519
Sit, sit, sit.

142
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,560
Sit.

143
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,240
What?

144
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,800
You'll know when you see it.

145
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:16,600
Wow.

146
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,759
See that?

147
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,879
Our home has 360-degree coverage with no blind spots.

148
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,240
Everything is monitored.

149
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,920
Gosh, so many.

150
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:25,720
Ruochu.

151
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,279
This is a critical time.

152
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,480
Let's not go out for a while.

153
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,680
As for school,

154
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,959
Just take sick leave.

155
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:31,680
Okay.

156
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,040
I understand.

157
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:35,800
Don't look so glum.

158
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:36,959
Look around.

159
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,199
Coming back to this apartment,

160
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,279
Do you like it?

161
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,319
I felt like before,

162
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:42,199
This apartment didn't look like this.

163
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:44,240
Last time, it was full of flowers.

164
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,839
This time, I almost didn't recognize it.

165
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,000
When the danger is over,

166
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,879
You can decorate it however you want.

167
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,319
As long as I'm with you,

168
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,800
Anything is fine.

169
00:07:59,480 --> 00:07:59,920
Me too.

170
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,560
But I didn't expect our living together again

171
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,000
To start with fleeing for safety.

172
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:06,079
Who said I'm living with you?

173
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,079
We haven't made up yet.

174
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:08,800
Wait, no.

175
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,079
Then I'm begging you.

176
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:13,759
Let's make up.

177
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,319
I beg you.

178
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,319
Please.

179
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,480
I'll think about it.

180
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,560
Honey.

181
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,320
Look at you.

182
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,759
Honey, no wonder you're a top student.

183
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,080
You've suspended your studies,

184
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,879
Yet you're still studying.

185
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,120
We just took leave.

186
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,320
It's not a suspension.

187
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,039
Besides, the teacher didn't promise

188
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:20,279
I could graduate without taking exams.

189
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,279
You know, I've lived two lives now.

190
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,440
I'm decades old inside.

191
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,279
I'm practically ready to retire.

192
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:43,480
And I have to take exams? Where's the justice?

193
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:45,600
Rebirth isn't an excuse for not studying.

194
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:48,799
Finish this test paper.

195
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,360
Where are you going?

196
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,559
To get some water.

197
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:53,879
I'm thirsty too.

198
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,159
I'm thirsty too.

199
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,200
So much stuff.

200
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,519
Yeah.

201
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,840
When did you buy all this?

202
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,919
I asked Brother Liang to Flash Deliver it.

203
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,720
Since I don't know how long we'll be stuck at home.

204
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,799
So I stocked up a bit.

205
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:08,120
What is "Flash Deliver"?

206
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,039
It's a type of home delivery service.

207
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,399
What is that?

208
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,799
You'll find out later.

209
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:16,399
Are you hungry?

210
00:10:16,919 --> 00:10:17,320
Yeah.

211
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,799
I'll cook something for you.

212
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,480
It smells so good.

213
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,919
When did you learn to stew beef brisket?

214
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,039
Back at the internet cafe.

215
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,480
You'd even burn instant noodles.

216
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:32,679
Does it smell good?

217
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,399
It smells amazing.

218
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,120
Have a taste.

219
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:35,559
Careful, it's hot.

220
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,200
Careful.

221
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,039
It's delicious.

222
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:45,559
From now on, all the meals at home...

223
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,600
...will be made by you, okay?

224
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,120
Sure.

225
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,440
Sure. As long as you want to eat,

226
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,799
I'll make anything for you.
